latestPosts.caption:
A love letter to banaras.... 
DEAR BANARAS🛕🪔🪷
 You're so beautiful and simple. Visiting you felt like the safe hug I needed....
I had always dreamed of finding a city where spiritualityy filled the air, and then I discovered you .... where spirituality was everywhere i turned 🕉️
The images I did capture don't do justice to the true essence of what one experiences here🛕⛵️
Your beauty and simplicity will stay with me forever, Thank you so much for everything🌼
Please call me again❣️

With love,
Manogya 🫀🧿
